title: 4. Lauren's Story: cystic acne, corporate skincare, professional philosophy and everything in between.
description: Hi everyone! This is Lauren and I am sharing my personal journey to my career in the skincare industry - how it started at a young age, weaved in and out of the industry, and landed now in the corporate skincare world. I hope you enjoy learning a bit more about my story, let me know what you think!
